The game will air on FOX at noon and can also be streamed on various platforms. The Titans are favored in the matchup, but the Bears are hoping to pull off an upset in their home opener. Fans can expect a competitive game with plenty of excitement as the 2024 NFL season gets underway.

name: Raiders
summary: The Raiders lost to the Chargers 22-10 in their season opener. Malcolm Koonce was one of three Raiders ruled out due to injury, while DeAndre Carter was also ruled out for the Chargers. Jim Harbaugh, the Raiders' new head coach, made his debut in the game. The Chargers' defense played well, holding the Raiders to just 10 points. Derwin James, a Chargers safety, said he was motivated to play well against the Raiders after they embarrassed him in a blowout loss last season. The Chargers are favored to win the rematch in Week 1, according to oddsmakers. The game will be televised on DAZN and will also be available to stream live on CBS News and Yahoo Sports.
